  "title": "Creative Designer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Taking design briefs to understand requirements</li>\n  <li>Conceptualising and developing design concepts, graphics and layouts</li>\n  <li>Conceptualising and creating brand visual style guides for various clients</li>\n  <li>Designing and producing online and offline collateral in accordance with brand guidelines</li>\n  <li>Presenting ideas, concepts and design solutions to various stakeholders and incorporating their feedback into the final design</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess at least a Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma in Arts/Design/Media Studies or related fields</li>\n  <li>A flair for creativity and have a keen eye for aesthetics in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Learn fast and work independently</li>\n  <li>Take pride &amp; responsibilities in own design works; achieving the best through reworking &amp; experimenting!</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills and can clearly communicate your ideas, designs and suggestions.</li>\n  <li>Strong team player who can collaborate effectively with different stakeholders</li>\n  <li>Possess good knowledge of design tools such as Adobe InDesign, Illustrator, Photoshop, Lightroom and Dreamweaver.</li>\n  <li>Having experience in motion graphics and video editing is a bonus!</li>\n</ul>",
