    "description": "<p>Our creative arm, Etereo (www.etereomedia.com) is a creative agency founded in Singapore.&nbsp;We specialise in branding, digital marketing and content creation. We’re in the business of creating growth for small companies, which we believe, strongly starts with branding. We&nbsp;take a tailor-made approach&nbsp;for every project from conception to completion.</p>\n<p>Why? Because no two companies are alike.</p>\n<p>At the start of every project, we customise a detailed project plan together with our clients to set expectations, ensure alignment, and define key milestones and deliverables. Experience tells us the best solutions are the ones co-ideated with clients. We incorporate your ideas with our broad level of expertise to create memorable experiences for your brands &amp; products.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
